We are pleased to share your Retainer Agreement for the matter of {{ $json.client_full_name }} v. {{ $json.defendant_name }} (accident on {{ $json.accident_date_formatted }} at {{ $json.accident_location }}).

{{ $json.injury_summary }}

Your Retainer Agreement is ready for review. Please download it securely here:
{{ $json.clio_document_url }}

To schedule your {{ $json.consultation_type }}, please use the following link: {{ $json.booking_link }}

Best regards,
Richards & Law

